The Phoenix ORM is an open-source library for PHP programming language.

You can find more information at the Phoenix ORM website at http://cygnuslab.com.ar/p/phoenix-orm/


Configuration / Setup
------------------------------------------------------------

include 'Db.php';
include 'Model.php';

Db::configure('host','localhost');
Db::configure('username','root');
Db::configure('password','');
Db::configure('name','database_name_here');
Db::configure('type','mysql');

Model::register('models/');
------------------------------------------------------------

A basic example
------------------------------------------------------------

$post = Posts::find(1);
echo $post->title;
------------------------------------------------------------